data.description: Clean, fresh, 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with amazing views! This property includes the lot to the north for a total of 1.1 acres plus or minus. Lots or room for toys and parking. The home has a newer roof and ac. New carpet to be installed on the first of sept. Fresh interior paint. Oversized garage that is fully insulated, drywall and ac. No need to fix up anything. Won't last call for your private showing. Shelving and table in garage, and garden grape vines and plants, and wooden outside gym, do not convey with sale.
